{"tid":1965023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國喊停今年度陸生來台　「考慮兩岸關係」","createTime":"2020-04-09T08:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T08:51:48.000Z","uid":239389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a75aaa01a98acb8064e95646911e345abdb908fb","tid":1965023,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T08:17:45.000Z","msg":"中國教育部決定暫停今年度陸生來台就讀工作，並稱是綜合考量新冠病毒（Covid-19，俗稱武漢肺炎）疫情及兩岸關係形勢，所做出的決定。<br />\n相關新聞：外資：Apple驗證快馬加鞭  9月2款iPhone 12先報到！<br />\n綜合中國媒體報導，中國教育部港澳台辦負責人表示，已在台灣高校就讀並願意繼續在台升讀的陸生，可依自願原則留在「島內」繼續升讀。<br />\n<br />\n綜合考慮疫情防控和兩岸關係，中方決定暫停2020年大陸各地各學歷層級畢業生赴台升讀工作。<br />\n<br />\n不過，大陸高校今年對台招生政策不變，中國教育部表示：「有關高校招生信息已在內地（祖國大陸）高校面向港澳台招生信息網發布」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n本新聞文字、照片、影片專供蘋果「升級壹會員」閱覽，版權所有，禁止任何媒體、社群網站、論壇，在紙本或網路部分引用、改寫、轉貼分享，違者必究。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200409/QRFE63E5YD2DAYA3LACUSBSTJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200409%2FQRFE63E5YD2DAYA3LACUSBSTJI%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=c21bde94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200409%2FQRFE63E5YD2DAYA3LACUSBSTJI%2F&h=408a32be\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200409/QRFE63E5YD2DAYA3LACUSBSTJI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣係咪又被迫獨立左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeff36b65ad84d26a7890c757b637a40a1307685","tid":1965023,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T08:51:48.000Z","msg":"推"}]}